  "keyFeatures": [
    "Snapshot testing for .NET with support for NUnit, xUnit, MSTest, TUnit, Fixie, and Expecto",
    "Automatic serialization of complex objects to human-readable text for comparison",
    "Smart scrubbing of non-deterministic values (GUIDs, dates, paths) for stable snapshots",
    "Integration with diff tools for visual review of snapshot changes",
    "Extensible plugin ecosystem with 60+ community extensions",
    "Parameterised test support with automatic file naming",
    "Custom converters for binary types (images, PDFs, Excel)",
    "CI/CD integration for uploading received files on build failure"
  ],
